org.tagaprice.server.dao.helper
Class DbSaveAssertUtility

java.lang.Object
  org.tagaprice.server.dao.helper.DbSaveAssertUtility

public class DbSaveAssertUtility
extends java.lang.Object

This class asserts that a given entity is saved in the database.

It does so by generating a SQL-statement to query the object and then asserts the retrieved resultSet. setSimpleJdbcTemplate(SimpleJdbcTemplate) must be called before the assert methods can be used.

Author:
haja
